        <p><span style="color:red;">Current containment procedures have failed to contain the proliferation of SCP-6298-1 instances. Research efforts have been diffused to all researchers specialising in noöspheric, semantospheric, and conceptual spaces. The SCP-6298 research project has been elevated to Alpha Priority. All available resources have been committed to the completion of the Conceptual Luxation and Organo-Semiotic Egress FilTer. When completed, the device will enable perfect semiotic isolation of all remaining individualised identities, and prevent all forms of interpersonal semantic dissolution.</p>


