        <p><s>Following confirmed transmission from SCP-6298-α to his remote attending physician, Dr. Joanna Hernandez, who had never interacted physically with SCP-6298-α, the dedicated research staff have reassessed the possible infection vectors. The most likely source of transmission is an unidentified memetic or infohazardous component to the SCP-6298 phenomenon, as the only evident connection between Hernandez and SCP-6298-α is mono-directional observation of the initially infected instance. Primary research efforts into the anomaly have been transferred to Site-82, and the containment procedures updated.</s></p>

